$ Makefile for the Base64 C++ library

This is the → development/make[Makefile] for my → development/Base64/Encoding-and-decoding-base-64-with-cpp[C++ base64 en- and decoder]. Currently, it compiles two libarary and its
→ development/Base64/Encoding-and-decoding-base-64-with-cpp/test[`test.cpp`] file with the → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/CPP standard C++11 and C++17. The latter is required to
test the → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/CPP-Standard-Library/string_view[`std::string_view`] interface.

